{
  "page": "House of Ullhor",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>House of Ullhor</b> is one of the slaving families of <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>. They reside in the <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid_of_Ullhor\" title=\"Pyramid of Ullhor\">pyramid of Ullhor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#House_of_Ullhor_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House of Ullhor at the end of the third century</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Household\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Household</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_Ullhor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_Ullhor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_mo_Ullhor\" title=\"Grazdan mo Ullhor\">Grazdan mo Ullhor</a>, one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Good_Masters\" title=\"Good Masters\">Good Masters</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a> who deals in <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a>, attends a meeting with <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>. He is also present the next day, when Daenerys arrives to take control over the Unsullied of the city. When she orders her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_Astapor\" title=\"Fall of Astapor\">attack</a> after taking possession of the Unsullied, Grazdan shouts for the Unsullied to defend the Good Masters. He is killed by Daenerys's <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodrider\" title=\"Bloodrider\">bloodrider</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Rakharo\" title=\"Rakharo\">Rakharo</a>, who puts an arrow through his mouth.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>One of Grazdan's former slaves, <a href=\"/index.php/Cleon\" title=\"Cleon\">Cleon</a>, later overthrows the <a href=\"/index.php/Ruling_council_of_Astapor\" title=\"Ruling council of Astapor\">ruling council of Astapor</a> installed by Daenerys, and installs himself as King of Astapor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_Ullhor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Following their failed attack against <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Astapor\" title=\"Siege of Astapor\">siege of Astapor</a>, the survivors of the battle hold a great feast in the <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid_of_Ullhor\" title=\"Pyramid of Ullhor\">pyramid of Ullhor</a>, ending the night by drinking <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poisoned</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_of_Ullhor_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House of Ullhor at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_Ullhor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House of Ullhor at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known members of the House of Ullhor during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>{<a href=\"/index.php/Grazdan_mo_Ullhor\" title=\"Grazdan mo Ullhor\">Grazdan mo Ullhor</a>}</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Household\">Household</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_Ullhor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Household\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>{<a href=\"/index.php/Cleon\" title=\"Cleon\">Cleon</a>}, an enslaved butcher</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_Ullhor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 30\">Chapter 30</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_71\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 71\">Chapter 71</a>, Daenerys VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Houses_of_Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Template:Houses of Slaver&#39;s Bay\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Houses_of_Slaver%27s_Bay&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Houses of Slaver&#39;s Bay (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Houses_of_Slaver%27s_Bay&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a